      "text": [
        " : قُلْتُ لِأَبِي عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ رَجُلٌ مَاتَ وَ تَرَكَ سِتَّةَ إِخْوَةٍ وَ جَدّاً قَالَ \"هُوَ كَأَحَدِهِمْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5643 - Ibn Abi Umayr narrated from Ibn Muskan from Abu Baṣir, who said: I asked Abu Abdullah (as) about a man who died and left behind six brothers and a grandfather.\nImam (as) said: \"The grandfather is considered as one of them.\""
        ]
      }
